data.description: The popular Sinclair floorplan features 4 bedrooms, three bathrooms, plus main floor flex room with open kitchen/dining/living room.  The large walk-in pantry accommodates all your big box store purchases, while the island and ample counterspace in the kitchen make cooking a breeze.  Walk-in closets in every bedroom, as well as oversized double or triple windows! The en suite bath in the primary bedroom features a beautiful freestanding soaking tub and separate shower.   Hunter Hills does not have an HOA.
